WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.048 --> 00:00:07.680
Once embodied in the power of workers councils, a power destined to supplant all the other powers worldwide

2
00:00:08.192 --> 00:00:10.496
the proletarian movement becomes its own product.

3
00:00:11.008 --> 00:00:15.104
This product is the producer himself and in his own eyes the producer himself

4
00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:16.896
has himself as his goal

5
00:00:17.408 --> 00:00:21.504
Only in this context can the Spectacle's negation of life be negated in its turn

6
00:00:24.576 --> 00:00:30.720
The Spectacle is not a collection of images rather it is a social relationship between people that is mediated by images

7
00:00:36.352 --> 00:00:43.264
The Spectacle is not a collection of images rather it is a social relationship between people that is mediated by

8
