As a part of society it is that sector where all attention, all consciousness converges

34
00:02:27.712 --> 00:02:33.600
Being isolated and precisely for that reason this sector is the locus of illusion and false consciousness

35
00:02:33.856 --> 00:02:38.208
The unity it imposes is merely the official language of generalized speculation

36
00:02:42.048 --> 00:02:48.192
The phenomenon of separation is part and parcel of the unity of the world, of a global social praxis that is split

37
00:02:48.448 --> 00:02:51.008
up into reality on the one hand and image on the other

38
00:02:51.264 --> 00:02:54.592
Social practice which the Spectacles autonomy challenges

39
00:02:55.104 --> 00:02:58.688
Is also the real totality to which the Spectacle is subordinate

40
00:02:58.944 --> 00:03:04.320
So deep is the rift in this totality however the Spectacle is able to emerge as its apparent goal

41
00:03:04.832 --> 00:03:09.440
The language of the Spectacle is composed of the signs of dominant organisation of production

42
00:03:09.952 --> 00:03:13.792
signs which are at the same time the ultimate end products of that organisation

43
00:03:16.096 --> 00:03:22.240
The Spectacle cannot be set in abstract opposition to concrete social activity, for the dichotomy between reality and image will

44
00:03:22.496 --> 00:03:25.056
survive on either side of any such distinction

45
00:03:25.568 --> 00:03:28.384
Thus the Spectacle, although it turns reality on his head

46
00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:30.688
is itself a product of real activity

47
00:03:30.944 --> 00:03:36.576
Likewise lived reality suffers the material assualtss of the Spectacles mechanisms of contemplation

48
00:03:36.832 --> 00:03:40.672
incorporating the spectacular order and lending that order positive support

49
00:03:41.184 --> 00:03:44.000
rach side therefore has its share of objective reality

50
00:03:44.256 --> 00:03:47.328
and every concept as it takes it's place on one side or the other

51
00:03:47.584 --> 00:03:50.912
has no foundation apart from its transformation into it's opposite

52
00:03:51.168 --> 00:03:54.240
reality erupts within the Spectacle and the Spectacle is real

53
00:03:54.752 --> 00:03:59.616
This reciprocal alienation is the essence and underpinning of society as it exists

54
00:04:02.176 --> 00:04:06.016
In a world that really has been turned on it's head, truth is a moment of falsehood

